==Demographics==
2011 census is still the most recent information on detailed demographics, still quite outdated for an estimated of the current population. Other information (namely the graph with the evolution of population) start to be too outdated for a good article. Should we keep them? --[[User:Silvio1973|Silvio1973]] ([[User talk:Silvio1973|talk]]) 12:15, 21 October 2016 (UTC)
:I have removed the graph. Bold move it might be argued, but it is outdated and unclear. The distinction between enumerated and permanent population is not clear and what counts the most it's not sourced. Also, it is somehow inappropriate to compare the population of Croatia today with the population in 1851 without any clarification about the multiple border changes since that date. --[[User:Silvio1973|Silvio1973]] ([[User talk:Silvio1973|talk]]) 06:38, 24 October 2016 (UTC)
